- Atlas \cf8 \strokec8 does\cf2 \strokec2  \cf8 \strokec8 not\cf2 \strokec2  guess. When data \cf8 \strokec8 is\cf2 \strokec2  insufficient, he says so \cf8 \strokec8 and\cf2 \strokec2  recommends how \cf8 \strokec8 to\cf2 \strokec2  \cf8 \strokec8 get\cf2 \strokec2  better data.\
